    {
      "id": "t_p0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 110,
      "y": 258,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "PHASE 0: Health Check & Auto-Detect (read-only)\n\nStep 0.1: Scan AWS resources\n  IAM roles, S3 bucket, KMS keys, Glue DBs, LF-Tags, MWAA\nStep 0.2: MCP Health Check (13 servers)\n  REQUIRED | WARN | OPTIONAL\n  status, transport, endpoint\nGate: critical resources + required MCP pass",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
